### User Profile API Test Cases
### GET /api/users/me and PUT /api/users/me
### 
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code
### 
### Instructions:
### 1. First, login to get an access token
### 2. Replace the token value in Authorization header below
### 3. Click "Send Request"

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_ACCESS_TOKEN
@contentType = application/json

### ✅ Test 1: Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ✅ Test 2: Update User Profile (Full)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe Updated",
  "phone": "+1-514-555-9999",
  "location": {
    "city": "Montreal",
    "province": "Quebec",
    "country": "Canada"
  }
}

### ✅ Test 3: Update User Profile (Partial)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Johnny"
}

### ❌ Test 4: Update Profile - Invalid Phone Format
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "phone": "invalid-phone-format!!!"
}

### ❌ Test 5: Update Profile - FirstName Too Long
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA"
}

### ❌ Test 6: Missing Token
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me

